Our team opened the doors to our Des Moines location in October of 2014.Learn more about Greenside Recreational - Des Moines, Opens a popupSpecialtiesGreenside Recreational is proud to be one of Seattle's first recreational marijuana facilities. Our team opened the doors to our Des Moines location in October of 2014.HistoryEstablished in 2014.Our history with the Seattle cannabis community began in Lake City as Greenside Medical in 2011. When recreational cannabis arrived in 2014, we became one of the very first cannabis retailers in Washington State with our Greenside Rec location in Des Moines.In 2016, our Seattle pot shop joined the recreational market and became Greenside Recreational. Greenside Rec Seattle experienced a devastating fire in early January of 2017. It was a tough few months for Greenside Rec Seattle, but the community support allowed our Lake City shop to bounce back. Construction is complete and our fresh and new Greenside Seattle shop is open for business in Lake City. Stop in and check out the new store with fresh products!We look forward to serving our community for many more years to come.Thanks for making history with us!
